# CCVAA source conventions

- App Router under `src/app/`; shared content in `src/lib/site.ts`
- Prefer Server Components; add `"use client"` only when needed
- Admin: keep `robots: noindex`; mail via `/admin/mail` proxy (do not iframe Hover directly)
- Admin session/auth helpers live under `src/app/api/admin/` and `src/lib/admin/` (mail-session, not OTP)
- Before new Next APIs: check `node_modules/next/dist/docs/`
- Edge/request interception: `src/proxy.ts`, not deprecated `middleware.ts`
